photos.alt: A photo of a view from a hill, with a bridge  going from the bottom right corner towards the center of the frame, followed by various buildings, then many trees with a cone roof peeking through them, and skyscrapers on the horizon. The photo is framed by an out-of-focus fir on the left, and there is a red tiled roof visible in the bottom right. The sky is grey with clouds.
